Animation.transition-colors: transition-property: background-color, border-color, color, fill, stroke;

Animations.set: @keyframes bounce { 0%, 100% { transform: translateY(-25%); animation-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.8,0,1,1); } 50% { transform: translateY(0); animation-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0,0,0.2,1); } }
@keyframes ping { 0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; } 75%, 100% { transform: scale(2); opacity: 0; } }

Background gradient.via-current: background-image: linear-gradient(to right, VAR(--tw-gradient-from), currentColor, VAR(--tw-gradient-to));

Background gradient.via-transparent: background-image: linear-gradient(to right, VAR(--tw-gradient-from), transparent, VAR(--tw-gradient-to));

Flexbox.space-x-7: --space-x-reverse: 0; margin-right: calc(1.75rem * var(--space-x-reverse)); margin-left: calc(1.75rem * calc(1 - var(--space-x-reverse)));

Flexbox.space-x-px: --space-x-reverse: 0; margin-right: calc(1px * var(--space-x-reverse)); margin-left: calc(1px * calc(1 - var(--space-x-reverse)));

Flexbox.space-y-px: --space-y-reverse: 0; margin-top: calc(1px * calc(1 - var(--space-y-reverse))); margin-bottom: calc(1px * var(--space-y-reverse));

Forms.focus-within: focus-within: { /* CSS properties to apply when a child element has focus */ };

Group hover.group-hover:text-white: The element will have white text when its parent group is hovered over.

Group hover.group-hover:bg-blue-500: The element will have a blue background when its parent group is hovered over.

Positioning.inset-auto: top: auto; right: auto; bottom: auto; left: auto;

Text.truncate: overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap;

Text.font-sans: font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';

Text.font-serif: font-family: Georgia, Cambria, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;

Text.font-mono: font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', 'Courier New', monospace;

Visibility.sr-only: position: absolute; width: 1px; height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: -1px; overflow: hidden; clip: rect(0, 0, 0, 0); white-space: nowrap; border-width: 0;

Visibility.not-sr-only: position: static; width: auto; height: auto; padding: 0; margin: 0; overflow: visible; clip: auto; white-space: normal; border-width: 0;
